"""
CUI Reduction System

Reduces extracted CUIs through filtering, hierarchy pruning,
coverage-based redundancy removal, relevance filtering, and
structural confidence scoring. Groups results via Louvain.

No Gemini API. No text embedding. No preferred term filtering.
Structural guards only. CUI-to-CUI relevance via anchor embeddings.
Otsu-driven thresholds throughout — zero hardcoded constants.
"""

